  "title": "Robustly Crunchy Turkish Avocado Wrap",
  "description": "A crunchy and tangy Turkish dish featuring avocado hass pulp, shio-cure, and ayurvedic-rajasic-friendly ingredients, all wrapped in a pandan leaf wrap.",
