      "amount": "1 small",
      "notes": "thinly sliced"
    },
    {
      "name": "cucumber",
      "amount": "1 medium",
      "notes": "sliced"
    },
    {
      "name": "turkish pepper",
      "amount": "1/2 teaspoon"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Prepare the shio-cure mixture by mixing it with lemon juice and letting it sit for 10 minutes.",
    "Cut the avocado in half and remove the pit.",
    "Spread a tablespoon of shio-cure mixture on each pandan leaf.",
    "Arrange a few slices of red onion and cucumber on each leaf.",
    "Place a half avocado on each leaf, then sprinkle with sumac and pistachios.",
    "Add a pinch of turkish pepper to each wrap.",
    "Fold the pandan leaves to enclose the filling, and serve immediately.",
    "Garnish with additional pistachios and sumac if desired."
